## EXPLICITLY OUT OF SCOPE FOR THIS MVP

To protect hackathon timelines, the following are explicitly not required unless trivial to include:
- Real bank/core-banking system integration
- Production-grade auth, multi-tenancy, or security hardening beyond basic good practice
- Real GST/alternative-data API integrations (synthetic data only)
- Horizontal scaling or high-availability infrastructure beyond Cloud Run defaults

If any of the above seem necessary to reach core objectives, flag this as an open question rather than silently building it.

